<h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Closed Beta: Patch 26 (Feb 24, 2014)</h4><ul><li>Health increased to 200, up from 150.</li><li>Magic Resistance increased to 40, up from 35.</li><li>Void II passive removed.</li><li>New Stackable Passive - Fervor: Taking damage from an enemy Shaper causes you to regenerate 40 Health over 10 seconds.</li><li>Cost increased to 1340, up from 1315.</li></ul><h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Closed Beta: Patch 5 (July 18, 2013)</h4><ul><li>Fixed an issue where the shield granted by this item was not activating again for the remainder of the game after it was fully removed once.</li></ul>